{"tid":2341193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男童被同窗一掌拍落碌架床，臉部墜地顱內出血受重傷","createTime":"2020-12-26T06:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T16:15:07.000Z","uid":38539,"like":304,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"d25db643ec08a9f5985d510df73a8ea1cf3eda88","tid":2341193,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7nPhSJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7nPhSJ.gif&h=718dcad8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國廣東省惠州市一名男童日前在托育機構內玩耍時，被其他同學從背後猛力一推，從上層床鋪倒栽墜落，臉部直接撞擊地板，造成顱內出血，所幸沒有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《網易新聞》報導，事發於12月21日中午，2名惠州東湖雙語學校的學生，當時與其他學生在一間私人托育機構的寢室內玩耍，2名學生在上鋪打鬧，其中一人似乎打算離開，但另一名學生這時突然從他後方猛力一推，被推的學生腳部勾到床框後變成倒栽墜落地面，嚇得其他學生趕緊過來察看情況。<br />\n<br />\n東湖雙語學校發聲明表示，該名學生墜落上鋪後造成顱內出血，經過搶救治療後，已經沒有生命危險，至於責任問題，2名學生的家長目前仍在和托育機構協調中。<br />\n<br />\n裡面有片<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201226/HC3FRF52BFH7FBDVLWZW2W43YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201226%2FHC3FRF52BFH7FBDVLWZW2W43YA%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=87965a1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201226%2FHC3FRF52BFH7FBDVLWZW2W43YA%2F&h=5852e885\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201226/HC3FRF52BFH7FBDVLWZW2W43YA/</a>"},{"pid":"b41e3041e294426c829498e85c824104091b61c3","tid":2341193,"uid":379150,"like":141,"dislike":4,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"斷頸重刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a758f85c1f9df3f3b991eaa13fccb438e2e515","tid":2341193,"uid":14103,"like":183,"dislike":5,"score":178,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"所幸沒有生命危險。<br />\n不冇眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset