103,"like":183,"dislike":5,"score":178,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"所幸沒有生命危險。<br />\n不冇眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"死唔係最慘<br />\n最慘係嗰啲死唔去但變咗弱智嗰啲<br />\n尤其是喺支那<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>「以前中學有次週會 個陣好似得中二/三<br />\n學校唔知係邊度請左班大陸黎既殘障人士<br />\n有啲係肢體有啲係智力咁啦<br />\n跟住逐個逐個係度講點解會殘障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始都係佢啲咩比人拐走呀老豆老母唔要個啲行野<br />\n講講下有個坐輪椅既話自己其實唔係智障亦都無殘疾<br />\n但係細個可能反應慢啲屋企人以為佢弱智<br />\n跟住比人送左入特殊學校<br />\n然後入到去比個智障既肥仔將佢由3樓扔左落街<br />\n所以佢就變左殘疾人士了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到一半已經完全忍唔撚到烏低身狂笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到啲老師開咪叫人唔好再笑」</blockquote><br />\n諗起呢段嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18381e1afe223ca9795b02c5fe57b6451216bcdc","tid":2341193,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"018472e572607c4e418cd5a174f5577cc0694be8","tid":2341193,"uid":133806,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"50a758f85c1f9df3f3b991eaa13fccb438e2e515","tid":2341193,"uid":14103,"like":183,"dislike":5,"score":178,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"所幸沒有生命危險。<br />\n不冇眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"死唔係最慘<br />\n最慘係嗰啲死唔去但變咗弱智嗰啲<br />\n尤其是喺支那<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>「以前中學有次週會 個陣好似得中二/三<br />\n學校唔知係邊度請左班大陸黎既殘障人士<br />\n有啲係肢體有啲係智力咁啦<br />\n跟住逐個逐個係度講點解會殘障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始都係佢啲咩比人拐走呀老豆老母唔要個啲行野<br />\n講講下有個坐輪椅既話自己其實唔係智障亦都無殘疾<br />\n但係細個可能反應慢啲屋企人以為佢弱智<br />\n跟住比人送左入特殊學校<br />\n然後入到去比個智障既肥仔將佢由3樓扔左落街<br />\n所以佢就變左殘疾人士了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到一半已經完全忍唔撚到烏低身狂笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到啲老師開咪叫人唔好再笑」</blockquote><br />\n諗起呢段嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29df38f4014d44081df8fca2c5b4993a5d680b9","tid":2341193,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ade372628b9bdcaf5c348e21257c09e077cdfe5","tid":2341193,"uid":294,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2